<document>
	<title>Misdiagnosis of neglect in a child with bleeding disorder and cystic
   fibrosis.</title>

	<author>Carpentieri-U.</author>
	<author>Gustavson-L-P.</author>
	<author>Haggard-M-E.</author>

	<source>South-Med-J. 1978 Jul. 71(7). P 854-5.</source>

	<abstract>This report describes a child in whom a bleeding disorder secondary
   to vitamin K deficiency led to a mistaken diagnosis of child
   neglect, which was eventually corrected to that of cystic fibrosis.</abstract>

